highlights.text: “Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 75 weeks straight.
Post Malone has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Better Now” is the highest at #1.
“Taste (feat. Offset)” by Tyga and Offset is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 70 spots at #62.
“Praise The Lord (Da Shine) (feat. Skepta)” by A$AP Rocky and Skepta is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #25.
